{"id":15153,"date":"2024-06-10T15:08:49","date_gmt":"2024-06-10T08:08:49","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=15153"},"modified":"2024-06-10T15:08:49","modified_gmt":"2024-06-10T08:08:49","slug":"hyundai-thanh-cong-trien-khai-chuong-trinh-uu-dai-dac-biet-trong-thang-6-2024","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-thanh-cong-trien-khai-chuong-trinh-uu-dai-dac-biet-trong-thang-6-2024\/","title":{"rendered":"Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng tri\u1ec3n khai ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong th\u00e1ng 6\/2024"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>T\u1eeb nay cho \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft 30\/06\/2024, Li\u00ean doanh \u00f4 t\u00f4 Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV) ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tri\u1ec3n khai ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u201cVui \u0111\u00f3n h\u00e8 \u2013 S\u1eafm xe Hyundai\u201d\u00a0\u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd Hyundai u\u1ef7 quy\u1ec1n tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c.<\/p>\n<p>Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, th\u00f4ng qua vi\u1ec7c ra m\u1eaft nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eabu xe m\u1edbi, \u0111a d\u1ea1ng ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac, ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng cao tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u xe \u00f4 t\u00f4 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Hyundai li\u00ean t\u1ee5c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh qua 3 gi\u1ea3i World Car Award, n\u0103m nay l\u00e0 n\u0103m th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m Hyundai vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-thanh-cong-trien-khai-chuong-trinh-uu-dai-dac-biet-trong-thang-6-2024\/fb-ad_1200x628_1200x628\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-15154\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-15154\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/FB-ad_1200x628_1200x628-1024x536.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1517\" height=\"794\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/FB-ad_1200x628_1200x628-1024x536.png 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/FB-ad_1200x628_1200x628-300x157.png 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/FB-ad_1200x628_1200x628-768x402.png 768w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/FB-ad_1200x628_1200x628-1536x804.png 1536w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/FB-ad_1200x628_1200x628-2048x1072.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1517px) 100vw, 1517px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>G\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft d\u00f2ng xe Hyundai Accent phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u1edbi l\u1eafp r\u00e1p t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng trang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/p>\n<p>Th\u00e1ng 6 n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ti\u00ean phong c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, tr\u1ebb trung, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u xu h\u01b0\u1edbng, c\u00f9ng m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd nh\u1ea5t cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng, Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam tri\u1ec3n khai ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u201cVui \u0111\u00f3n h\u00e8 \u2013 S\u1eafm xe Hyundai\u201d v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i l\u00ean t\u1edbi 50% l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1. Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng\u00a0cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft ng\u00e0y 30\/06\/2024 t\u1ea1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd \u1ee7y quy\u1ec1n Hyundai tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c.<\/p>\n<p>Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng mua m\u1ed9t trong c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe Hyundai Custin, Elantra, Accent (2023), Venue v\u00e0 Grand i10 (2023), s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u01b0\u1edfng 1 trong 2 g\u00f3i \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho c\u00e1c xe nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 G\u00f3i 1: \u01afu \u0111\u00e3i l\u00e3i su\u1ea5t tr\u1ea3 g\u00f3p ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb 0% trong 12 th\u00e1ng<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 G\u00f3i 2: G\u00f3i h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh l\u00ean t\u1edbi 50% L\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1<\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng mua Grand i10 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eb7ng 1 n\u0103m B\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m v\u1eadt ch\u1ea5t trong th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<p>Trong \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c m\u1ee9c l\u00e3i su\u1ea5t \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i khi mua c\u00e1c xe n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng vay mua xe t\u1ea1i Ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n Ngo\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (VCB), Ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng Th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n Qu\u1ed1c T\u1ebf Vi\u1ec7t Nam (VIB),\u00a0\u00a0Ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng TMCP Th\u1ecbnh V\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n (PG Bank)\u00a0v\u00e0\u00a0Ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng Th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n Vi\u1ec7t Nam Th\u1ecbnh V\u01b0\u1ee3ng (VPB).<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn mua xe Hyundai Santa Fe ho\u1eb7c Hyundai Santa Fe Hybrid s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh khuy\u1ebfn m\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n<figure class=\"table\">\n<table style=\"height: 941px;\" width=\"1046\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>STT<\/td>\n<td>Phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n<\/td>\n<td>M\u1ee9c khuy\u1ebfn m\u1ea1i (VND)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1<\/td>\n<td>Santa Fe 2.2 D\u1ea7u<\/td>\n<td>70.000.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2<\/td>\n<td>Santa Fe 2.2 D\u1ea7u cao c\u1ea5p<\/td>\n<td>75.000.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3<\/td>\n<td>Santa Fe 2.5 X\u0103ng<\/td>\n<td>70.000.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4<\/td>\n<td>Santa Fe 2.5\u00a0 X\u0103ng cao c\u1ea5p<\/td>\n<td>75.000.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5<\/td>\n<td>Santa Fe Hybrid<\/td>\n<td>100.000.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/figure>\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eabu xe kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1c g\u00f3i \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i ri\u00eang t\u1eeb Hyundai H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>T\u1eeb nay cho \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft 30\/06\/2024, Li\u00ean doanh \u00f4 t\u00f4 Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV) ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tri\u1ec3n khai ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u201cVui \u0111\u00f3n h\u00e8 \u2013 S\u1eafm xe Hyundai\u201d\u00a0\u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd Hyundai u\u1ef7 quy\u1ec1n tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c. Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, th\u00f4ng qua vi\u1ec7c ra [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":15154,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"yst_prominent_words":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15153"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\